{"tid":1807714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府想架空區議會","createTime":"2020-01-02T03:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:19:51.000Z","uid":74182,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e8ca6b38b1d65a8c677f15244626c75422919c","tid":1807714,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"0006 #區議會 #落選建制派 #民政事務處 #分區委員會<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》接獲消息指，民政事務處屬下63個分區委員會，將各增設5名委員席位，並由建制派落選者出任。民政事務總署回覆查詢時未有直接否認，僅稱仍在擬備新一屆委員名單。有區議員擔心分區會日後或架空區議會，直接與政府合辦地區活動；有區議員則指政府做法旨在讓街坊有錯覺，認為該人士仍然有權力服務社區的「幻象」，維持地區「樁腳」作用。<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200102/60436587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60436587&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOADe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=f4b6e6bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200102%2F60436587&h=c1fb51cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200102/60436587</a>"},{"pid":"e55593772d4c673883f19404e0bcb0ed9d8dd934","tid":1807714,"uid":94344,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:18:07.000Z","msg":"所以獨立係唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左貼文宣，仲可以試下呢個 零成本方法<br />\n<br />\n👇👇👇<br />\n請幫推，連儂牆 外既新動員方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806977</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"40653baac5ecd333084d497635073c788e75ea28","tid":1807714,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2c8d0f3330b1f4130c5d41898285492ff49e8d","tid":1807714,"uid":18477,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"repl